OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe showers
OL,6,Fwill soon clear through the evening to
OL,7,Fleave the night dry with increasing
OL,8,Fclear periods. This together with the
OL,9,Fwind falling light will bring a patchy
OL,10,Finland frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FThe morning will be mostly dry
OL,13,Fwith bright, sunny spells. Cloud and
OL,14,Fscattered showers spread northeast
OL,15,Fduring the afternoon, these heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
